sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant AuthServer as Auth Server
    participant ResourceServer as Resource Server

    User->>App: Opens application
    App->>AuthServer: Redirect to /authorize (client_id, redirect_uri, scope, state)
    Note over User,AuthServer: User authenticates with Auth Server
    User->>AuthServer: Submits credentials (username, password)
    AuthServer-->>App: Redirect to redirect_uri with authorization_code + state
    App->>AuthServer: POST /token (authorization_code, client_id, client_secret)
    AuthServer-->>App: 200 OK { access_token, refresh_token, expires_in }
    App->>ResourceServer: GET /resource (Authorization: Bearer access_token)
    ResourceServer-->>App: 200 OK { protected data }
